<h4>
    What is gravity?
</h4>


<ul class = 'principleList'>
    <li>
        According to Newton's Law of Universal Gravitation,
        all objects with mass are attracted to all other objects with mass.
    </li>
    <li>
        Gravity is always an attraction between <strong>two</strong> objects.
        It exists only if there are two objects.
    </li>
    <li>
        Gravity attracts you to towards the earth
        because the earth has such a large mass.
    </li>
</ul>

